OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fheavy rain spreading northeastwards.
OL,7,FBecoming largely dry overnight with
OL,8,Fsome lighter rain lingering over the
OL,9,FIsles. Strong to gale force
OL,10,Fsoutheasterly winds easing inland
OL,11,Flater in the night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FOutbreaks of rain possible
OL,14,Fover the Isles but for many a dry day
OL,15,Fwith some bright or sunny spells.
OL,16,FBreezy inland with strong winds around
OL,17,Fthe coast, risk of gales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
